OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fand settled. Rather cloudy, although
OL,7,Foccasional breaks in the cloud will
OL,8,Fallow for some fine spells. A little
OL,9,Fbreezy near the coasts. A warm night
OL,10,Ffor some otherwise.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA fine day with light winds
OL,13,Fand almost uninterrupted sunshine,
OL,14,Fthough it may turn hazy at times.
OL,15,FTemperatures will become widely warm
OL,16,For very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
