OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSome
OL,6,Fcloudy periods on Tuesday, turning
OL,7,Fsunnier on Wednesday and Thursday,
OL,8,Fremaining mostly dry throughout.
OL,9,FBecoming hot in places as temperatures
OL,10,Fincrease.
